      <hr /><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1><span>088</span> - <span>Report Number</span><span> (R)</span></h1>
      <hr />
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - full</div>
      <div class="datename">April 2015</div>
      <hr />
      <table width="100%" class="indicators">
         <tr>
            <th width="45%"> First Indicator </th>
            <th width="45%"> Second Indicator </th>
         </tr>
         <tr>
            <td><em>Undefined</em><br /><span># - Undefined</span><br /><br /></td>
            <td><em>Undefined</em><br /><span># - Undefined</span><br /><br /></td>
         </tr>
      </table>
      <hr />
      <table width="100%" class="subfields">
         <tr>
            <td width="50%"></td>
            <td width="50%"></td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
            <th colspan="2">Subfield Codes</th>
         </tr>
         <tr>
            <td>
               <ul class="nomark">
                  <li>$a - Report number<span> (NR)</span></li>
                  <li>$z - Canceled/invalid report number<span> (R)</span></li>
               </ul>
            </td>
            <td>
               <ul class="nomark">
                  <li>$6 - Linkage<span> (NR)</span></li>
                  <li>$8 - Field link and sequence number<span> (R)</span></li>
               </ul>
            </td>
         </tr>
      </table>
      <hr />
      <h3>FIELD DEFINITION AND SCOPE</h3>
      <div class="definition">
         <div>
            <p>Report number that is not a Standard Technical Report Number (STRN), recorded in field
               027.
            </p>
         </div>
         <div>
            <p>Field 088 is repeated for multiple report numbers, except when one number is the canceled
               or invalid number corresponding to a valid report number.
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
      <hr />
      <h3>GUIDELINES FOR APPLYING CONTENT DESIGNATORS</h3>
      <div class="guidelines">
         <h4><span class="box">■</span> INDICATORS
         </h4>
         <div class="indicators">
            <ul>
               <li>Both indicator positions are undefined; each contains a blank (#).</li>
            </ul>
         </div>
         <h4><span class="box">■</span> SUBFIELD CODES
         </h4>
         <div class="subfields">
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$a - Report number</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div class="example">
                     <table>
                        <tr>
                           <td><strong>088</strong></td>
                           <td colspan="9"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>STRATLAB-71-98
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                           <td><strong>088</strong></td>
                           <td colspan="9"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>EPA-6001/2-76-224
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                     </table>
                  </div>
                  <div class="example">
                     <table>
                        <tr>
                           <td><strong>088</strong></td>
                           <td colspan="9"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>APA 3009
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                           <td><strong>088</strong></td>
                           <td colspan="9"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>APA 3010
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                           <td><strong>088</strong></td>
                           <td colspan="9"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>APA 3011
                           </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                           <td>490</td>
                           <td colspan="9">1#$aDocument ;$vno. 3009-3011</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                           <td>830</td>
                           <td colspan="9">#0$aDocument (Susitna Hydroelectric Project) ;$vno. 3009-3011.</td>
                        </tr>
                     </table>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$z - Canceled/invalid report number</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>Each canceled or invalid report number is contained in a separate subfield
                  $z. If no valid report number exists, only subfield $z
                  should be recorded.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="example">
                     <table>
                        <tr>
                           <td><strong>088</strong></td>
                           <td colspan="9"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>NASA-RP-1124-REV-3 <strong>$z</strong>NASA-RP-1124-REV-2 <em><span><br /><span>[One valid report number has been canceled in favor of another]</span></span></em></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                           <td><strong>088</strong></td>
                           <td colspan="9"><strong>##</strong><strong>$z</strong>NASA-TN-D-8008<em><span><br /><span>[Report number is invalid due to an error in assignment or printing on the
                                       item]</span></span></em></td>
                        </tr>
                     </table>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$6 - Linkage</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="//www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control
                              Subfields</a></em>.
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$8 - Field link and sequence number</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="//www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control
                              Subfields</a></em>.
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      <hr />
      <h3>CONTENT DESIGNATOR HISTORY</h3>
      <div class="history">
         <div>
            <p>Prior to 2015, series report numbers were included in fields 490/830, not in field
               088.
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
